<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" dir="ltr">
  <head>
    <title>IgAN Pathogenesis & Disease Progression Simulation</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Learn more about the IgAN 4-hit cascade and the role of APRIL. Use interactive hypothetical patient cases to simulate the risk of disease progression">
    {{> templates/header }}
    <link href="./styles.bundle.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
  </head>
  <body>
  <!-- Google Tag Manager (noscript) -->
<noscript><iframe src="https://www.googletagmanager.com/ns.html?id=GTM-WZLFQZR3"
height="0" width="0" style="display:none;visibility:hidden"></iframe></noscript>
<!-- End Google Tag Manager (noscript) -->
    <main class="wrapper" data-page-id="home" data-path-level="0">

      {{> templates/interstitial }}
      {{> templates/nav }}

      <div class="home-content-container content-container">
        <div class="header-box">
          <h1 class="yellow-header">欢迎访问 IgA肾病模拟平台</h1>
          <h2 class="subhead">在这里，您可深入了解 IgA肾病的发病机制&#65292; <br>以及患者真实的病程轨迹</h2>
        </div>
  
        <div class="flex">
          <div class="path-container">
            <h3>疾病机制</h3>
            <p>探秘分子机制：IgA肾病在分子层面如何启动&#65292; 以及病情如何逐步进展。</p>
  
            <div class="cta button nav-el" data-nav-url="pathogenesis/index">
              <p>了解更多</p>
              <img class="arrow" src="./assets/images/arrow-white.svg" alt="White arrow pointing right"/>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="path-container">
            <h3>疾病进程</h3>
            <p>走近 3 位虚拟患者：看看他们如何确诊 IgA肾病&#65292; 以及预后情况如何。</p>
  
            <div class="cta button nav-el" data-nav-url="progression/index">
              <p>了解更多</p>
              <img class="arrow" src="./assets/images/arrow-white.svg" alt="White arrow pointing right"/>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      {{> templates/footer-el }}

    </main>

    <script type="text/javascript" src="./static.bundle.js" charset="utf-8"></script>
  </body>
</html>